What Bosly Is
Bosly is a digital butler—an AI-powered personal operating system. Messages come in → Bosly classifies them → they become tasks, calendar events, or invoices → user acts. The app is designed for anyone to manage their digital life: a gardener, a freelancer, a parent.
Beneath the application layer, Bosly is a liberation architecture disguised as a productivity app. The mission: empower every individual to control their own data. No government database. No corporate cloud. Not even Bosly's creator.
Tagline: Your digital butler, in accord.
