 April 19, 2026: Browser vs Curl Reality
A subtle bug was discovered and documented: browsers reject Set-Cookie from 303 redirect responses, while curl does not. This was the root cause of a two-week "Session expired" bug. The fix changed the API to return 200 JSON with redirectTo and client-side router.push(). Bosly Gov learnt its first lesson: always check the Application tab for cookies before concluding "backend works."
